{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we could sit up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at night, they would let us come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was totally pitch black.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a grave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at the beginning, my mother would tell me stories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, she afterwards told me she told me every book she ever read, every movie she ever read.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But after a while, I guess she started sort of running out of stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever the reason was, they also lowered food to us once a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My days and nights got mixed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when she was awake, [POINTING] I was asleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was awake, she was asleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I retreated into this total fantasy world, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just lived in this make-believe world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it got to the point where I lost all touch with reality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just-- I just left this world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you recall anything about this fantasy world at this point in your life?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it started out where I was thinking mostly about my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was gonna find him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was gonna come and get me out of here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was that kind of thinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after a while-- I don't know what I was thinking of-- but it was-- I was out of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were there a few months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it got to the point where the-- this-- my mother tells me this, that the people-- these peasants said to her that the devil possessed me; she should kill me or something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she decided that she just had to get me out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just-- I wasn't eating and I-- And-- and I was in just-- I didn't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to some village.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
